ZA.name: Super Mario Maker™
ZA.description: With a practically infinite number of courses, Super Mario Maker – only available on Wii U – is packed with endless Mario fun everyone can enjoy! Visit amiibo.nintendo.eu for compatible amiibo™ and the latest information. The release of Super Mario Maker™ is accompanied by a Super Mario Maker Artbook. For fans who download Super Mario Maker from Nintendo eShop, a PDF of the Artbook is available on Nintendo's official Super Mario Maker website. (www.nintendo.co.uk/supermariomaker)
